    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is just so quiet now. i keep walking into the kitchen thinking i'll hear his collar jingle or see him waiting by the bowl, but then it hits me all over again that he's not coming back. the house feels so heavy and empty. i don't even know why i bother getting up in the morning anymore.",
